WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.350 --> 02:49.980
[Episode 13]

02:50.640 --> 02:51.760
I'll go with you.

02:51.760 --> 02:52.560
No.

02:53.050 --> 02:53.610
Master.

02:53.630 --> 02:54.630
You haven't recovered yet,

02:54.660 --> 02:55.660
so you mustn't risk it.

02:55.680 --> 02:57.170
I'm fine now.

02:57.200 --> 02:59.140
You guys are making me look like a loser.

03:02.850 --> 03:04.850
Fan Yue is never a loser,

03:04.880 --> 03:07.180
nor would he ever see himself as one.

03:07.210 --> 03:08.810
Don't you ever say something like that again.

03:09.520 --> 03:10.990
Then let me go with you.

03:13.650 --> 03:14.530
I know that

03:14.550 --> 03:16.350
entering the palace this time is fraught with danger.

03:16.380 --> 03:17.780
But how could you expect me to watch you

03:17.810 --> 03:18.870
risk your life?

03:18.910 --> 03:20.590
Have you considered my feelings?

03:23.990 --> 03:24.910
If you stay silent,

03:25.890 --> 03:26.940
that means you agree.

03:34.530 --> 03:35.650
Tian Huo is not here.

03:35.680 --> 03:36.960
No, don't!

03:39.150 --> 03:40.450
I'm not looking for Tian Huo.

03:41.170 --> 03:42.610
I'm here for Ms. Bai.

03:42.630 --> 03:43.150
You...

03:43.180 --> 03:43.980
Looking for me?

03:44.650 --> 03:45.490
Ms. Bai,

03:45.510 --> 03:47.070
thank you for saving my life last night.

03:47.100 --> 03:48.860
I, Mu Jiu, always return favors.

03:52.180 --> 03:53.390
This second Heart Flame...

03:53.560 --> 03:54.470
I'll give it to you.

03:54.500 --> 03:55.560
Consider it as repaying your kindness.

03:57.890 --> 03:59.310
I’ll take you up on that then.

04:04.170 --> 04:05.600
Huo, do you think...

04:05.920 --> 04:07.600
I'm a generous person?

04:10.780 --> 04:11.540
By the way,

04:11.620 --> 04:13.170
you guys were talking about...

04:13.190 --> 04:13.940
the Underground Palace.

04:14.380 --> 04:15.140
This is it, right?

04:17.800 --> 04:19.839
You eavesdropped on us again?

04:19.860 --> 04:20.700
No.

04:20.730 --> 04:21.649
I didn't mean it.

04:21.670 --> 04:22.630
I happen to hear it

04:22.660 --> 04:23.580
when I came to deliver the Heart Flame.

04:24.120 --> 04:24.760
I swear

04:24.780 --> 04:25.840
I will never tell anyone.

04:25.840 --> 04:27.390
Itching for trouble again, aren't you?

04:27.420 --> 04:28.500
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

04:28.520 --> 04:29.880
I'm here to help you.

04:29.910 --> 04:30.640
Really!

04:30.660 --> 04:31.700
How'll you help?

04:31.730 --> 04:32.610
Wait.

04:33.760 --> 04:35.390
Are you serious about helping?

04:37.120 --> 04:38.170
Of course.

04:38.650 --> 04:40.090
When we were in Rong Xian's realm of resentment,

04:40.110 --> 04:40.960
we were...

04:40.980 --> 04:42.980
inseparable as we faced life and death together.

04:43.490 --> 04:44.010
Right, Huo?

04:44.040 --> 04:45.400
Quit pretending to be friendly.

04:45.420 --> 04:47.020
Tian Huo didn't even enter the realm of resentment.

04:47.040 --> 04:48.280
We don't need your help.

04:48.310 --> 04:49.770
We need his help.

04:55.280 --> 04:57.020
That pesky fox is so annoying.

04:57.040 --> 04:57.930
And yet, Bai Shuo

04:57.960 --> 04:59.120
believed his nonsense.

04:59.610 --> 05:00.810
Don't worry about him, Mu Jiu.

05:00.840 --> 05:02.160
Just remember,

05:02.210 --> 05:03.570
no matter what happens tonight,

05:03.600 --> 05:05.480
you must protect Master.

05:05.500 --> 05:06.140
Understood.

05:06.840 --> 05:08.560
Actually, our master hasn't been

05:08.600 --> 05:10.060
happy all these years.

05:10.090 --> 05:10.990
It'd be nice

05:11.010 --> 05:12.230
if he can maintain

05:12.820 --> 05:13.740
this disposition.

05:13.770 --> 05:14.930
There are no "what if's" in this world.

05:16.120 --> 05:17.800
If our master hadn't forsaken

05:17.800 --> 05:19.480
his former innocence,

05:20.430 --> 05:22.140
he wouldn't have lived to this day.

05:28.240 --> 05:29.240
M-Master.

05:29.260 --> 05:29.680
I...

05:29.710 --> 05:30.670
I was talking nonsense just now.

05:30.690 --> 05:31.450
Regardless of how you may be,

05:31.480 --> 05:32.040
I will still like you

05:32.060 --> 05:33.360
and be loyal to you.

05:33.409 --> 05:35.050
What was Fan Yue like before?

05:37.050 --> 05:38.010
How did Fan Yue

05:38.090 --> 05:39.670
fall in love with Bai Shuo?

05:40.800 --> 05:41.490
Fall in...

05:41.580 --> 05:42.620
love?

05:49.190 --> 05:50.520
This is the entire process of how

05:50.520 --> 05:51.920
you got to know Bai Shuo.

05:52.530 --> 05:54.890
From Unbridled Pavilion to Bright Moon Palace,

05:54.920 --> 05:56.030
to Lanling,

05:56.050 --> 05:57.810
and now in Outlanders' City,

05:58.050 --> 06:00.170
I can't tell at which part did you fall in love.

06:00.320 --> 06:00.920
Master.

06:00.940 --> 06:01.900
Don't be fooled by her.

06:03.210 --> 06:05.020
Are you sure you didn't miss out on any details?

06:05.460 --> 06:06.700
Absolutely not.

06:06.730 --> 06:07.600
Master.

06:07.850 --> 06:08.930
Regardless,

06:08.950 --> 06:10.220
we had something to do with

06:10.250 --> 06:12.130
Bai Shuo's father's death.

06:12.150 --> 06:14.620
Although we may be allies with Bai Shuo now,

06:14.640 --> 06:16.800
it's only so that we can activate the Contemplation Stone.

06:16.830 --> 06:18.030
Sooner or later,

06:18.050 --> 06:19.840
we and Bai Shuo are bound to go our separate ways.

06:39.900 --> 06:40.810
Xi.

06:40.830 --> 06:42.909
Fenlan Banquet is happening tonight.

06:43.060 --> 06:45.780
Love, hate, kill, greed.

06:45.810 --> 06:47.740
I don't know which Contemplation is next,

06:47.850 --> 06:52.909
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

06:48.260 --> 06:50.210
or what might actually happen.

06:50.830 --> 06:52.270
No matter what threats lie ahead,

06:52.290 --> 06:53.420
I'm not afraid.

06:54.230 --> 06:55.600
But Fan Yue...

06:55.970 --> 07:01.830
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

06:58.800 --> 06:59.850
I only remember you.

07:00.770 --> 07:01.870
You're the one who saved me

07:03.050 --> 07:03.890
and treats me well.

07:04.530 --> 07:11.980
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

07:07.960 --> 07:08.680
Be careful!

07:08.680 --> 07:10.080
Blocking the knife for me?

07:10.080 --> 07:11.760
You could have died, you know?

07:11.790 --> 07:12.740
I'm fine.

07:12.610 --> 07:17.800
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

07:12.760 --> 07:14.240
I said I would protect you.

07:14.880 --> 07:15.680
I won't forget

07:16.180 --> 07:16.980
these words.

07:18.350 --> 07:19.460
Luckily,

07:20.260 --> 07:21.600
I still have you.

07:22.100 --> 07:25.660
♫Across thousands of miles♫

07:23.500 --> 07:24.810
He's the Demon King of the Polar Region.

07:24.960 --> 07:26.840
He couldn't let his guard down.

07:26.860 --> 07:27.960
We demons

07:28.040 --> 07:30.360
fought among a mountain of corpses and a sea of blood.

07:30.380 --> 07:32.140
You will never understand

07:30.430 --> 07:35.090
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

07:32.170 --> 07:33.740
what our master has been through.

07:37.810 --> 07:44.890
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

07:46.060 --> 07:50.680
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

07:56.170 --> 07:57.370
Must you enter the palace?

07:58.790 --> 07:59.870
I have to go.

08:01.080 --> 08:02.640
Is it because of the Contemplation Stone?

08:04.150 --> 08:05.120
Some things speak for themselves,

08:05.120 --> 08:06.600
even if you don't mention them.

08:07.290 --> 08:08.700
You chose to travel with the demons because

08:08.740 --> 08:10.820
you wanted to gather the Five Contemplations and become stronger, right?

08:12.000 --> 08:14.120
Is the next Contemplation here in Outlanders' City?

08:16.660 --> 08:17.460
Yes.

08:17.990 --> 08:19.830
Ultimately, this is my own problem.

08:20.690 --> 08:21.570
Chong Zhao.

08:22.690 --> 08:24.840
I know you don’t care about that Wutong Spirit Pill.

08:24.990 --> 08:25.950
Just stay here in the inn.

08:25.970 --> 08:27.180
Don't go and risk yourself.

08:27.300 --> 08:28.700
You may have things you want to do,

08:28.730 --> 08:30.580
and the Eternals are not willing to support you.

08:30.720 --> 08:31.470
Shuo.

08:32.610 --> 08:33.610
But, I will.

08:35.900 --> 08:36.740
So,

08:38.200 --> 08:39.620
what’s your plan for tonight?

08:48.060 --> 08:49.920
Who was it who said the Outlander Palace was dangerous,

08:49.920 --> 08:51.200
but is still going anyway?

08:54.690 --> 08:55.490
Let's go.

08:55.520 --> 08:56.380
Bei Chen.

08:56.970 --> 08:58.850
You know the Outlander Palace would be dangerous,

08:58.880 --> 08:59.980
yet you're still going?

09:00.060 --> 09:01.050
Ms. Bai.

09:01.330 --> 09:02.570
I know you mean well.

09:03.930 --> 09:06.260
But Kunlun collapsed a thousand years ago.

09:06.350 --> 09:07.510
Although it has been rebuilt,

09:07.530 --> 09:09.590
we have yet to regain our vitality.

09:09.760 --> 09:11.650
Kunlun needs the Wutong Spirit Pill.

09:11.850 --> 09:13.250
I'm here by order of my master.

09:13.280 --> 09:14.480
Although I know there's not much hope,

09:14.500 --> 09:15.640
I can't just give up.

09:15.670 --> 09:17.270
I'll do my best.

09:26.930 --> 09:28.410
You won't be able to talk them out of it.

09:28.850 --> 09:30.890
The disciples of Kunlun never let their master down.

09:31.020 --> 09:32.260
Aren't you the same?

09:32.600 --> 09:33.960
The responsibility of Lanling

09:33.980 --> 09:35.520
has always rested with you, hasn't it?

09:41.400 --> 09:42.280
Let's go.

09:42.840 --> 09:43.950
We should set off.

09:53.500 --> 09:54.860
I'll be alright entering the palace myself.

09:54.890 --> 09:56.050
You all should stay here in the inn.

09:56.990 --> 09:58.750
You think there's danger?

09:58.770 --> 10:00.940
If we don't come back in four hours,

10:01.020 --> 10:02.140
don't hesitate.

10:02.170 --> 10:04.010
Leave Outlanders' City immediately and report it to our master.

10:05.450 --> 10:06.650
Yes.

10:21.440 --> 10:23.120
[Peace and joy]

10:52.080 --> 10:53.650
Today is the Fenlan Festival.

10:54.080 --> 10:55.440
There are no longer deities in this world.

10:55.460 --> 10:56.660
Who are they making their wishes to?

10:57.200 --> 10:58.260
To themselves.

10:59.880 --> 11:01.840
The Outlanders were abandoned by the various races,

11:02.010 --> 11:03.660
and had no deity to pray to.

11:03.750 --> 11:05.590
By writing their wishes on the latern,

11:03.950 --> 11:05.210
[Fortune]

11:05.620 --> 11:07.220
they are reminding themselves to

11:07.820 --> 11:09.540
rely on no one but themselves for whatever they desire.

11:11.010 --> 11:11.930
That's right.

11:12.140 --> 11:13.240
Indeed, in this world,

11:13.540 --> 11:15.400
it's better to rely on yourself than to depend on others.

11:16.450 --> 11:17.360
Shuo.

11:17.720 --> 11:19.220
Let's go set off a sky lantern too.

11:21.620 --> 11:22.340
Okay.

11:22.360 --> 11:24.180
It's not yet time for the banquet anyway.

11:29.440 --> 11:30.240
[Contemplation]

11:30.240 --> 11:31.860
[Contemplation] [Peace]

11:34.140 --> 11:35.240
Take it.

11:38.370 --> 11:39.040
This is yours.

11:39.040 --> 11:39.720
Thank you.

11:47.300 --> 11:48.520
What did you write?

11:48.670 --> 11:49.510
Nothing.

11:50.740 --> 11:52.550
Someone as cold-hearted as you has secrets too?

12:15.210 --> 12:17.140
If it weren't for this moment

12:17.230 --> 12:19.160
and the tough battle ahead,

12:19.330 --> 12:21.250
this would be the most memorable scene

12:21.420 --> 12:23.500
I've ever witnessed.

12:29.720 --> 12:30.560
Shuo.

12:32.660 --> 12:33.780
We're not lovers.

12:37.940 --> 12:38.680
Right?

12:40.850 --> 12:42.330
I've asked Cang Shan

12:43.170 --> 12:44.570
how we got to know each other.

12:47.380 --> 12:48.500
-Actually...
-I’m sorry.

12:51.550 --> 12:53.100
About everything that has happened before.

12:53.860 --> 12:54.980
And also,

12:55.620 --> 12:56.580
regarding your father...

13:00.230 --> 13:01.150
I'm sorry.

13:04.420 --> 13:06.060
How I wish I am not him,

13:07.490 --> 13:09.220
but how I also wish I am him.

13:10.610 --> 13:12.210
At least he can protect you.

13:17.490 --> 13:18.690
How beautiful!

13:18.770 --> 13:20.080
Fireworks!

13:23.200 --> 13:24.180
So beautiful.

13:32.890 --> 13:34.010
It's time to enter the palace.

13:34.200 --> 13:35.130
Shuo.

13:38.710 --> 13:40.830
I don't know when he'll be back.

13:41.650 --> 13:42.610
But for now,

13:43.690 --> 13:44.970
let's say our goodbyes.

13:52.720 --> 13:57.730
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

14:00.620 --> 14:04.230
♫You are the light I yearn for♫

14:05.170 --> 14:09.400
♫You are my determined way home♫

14:09.480 --> 14:15.750
♫Let this moment stay forever♫

14:15.830 --> 14:19.860
♫I'm hugging you in the crowd♫

14:20.290 --> 14:22.750
♫Let's never let go♫

14:23.460 --> 14:25.820
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

14:49.030 --> 14:50.510
Are you angry?

14:51.270 --> 14:51.760
Just now, I...

14:51.760 --> 14:53.280
What happened just now?

14:54.090 --> 14:55.050
I don't remember.

14:56.800 --> 14:57.520
Anyway,

14:57.540 --> 14:59.060
remember what I told you.

14:59.090 --> 15:00.530
If you ever find yourself in danger again,

15:00.550 --> 15:01.990
protect yourself first.

15:02.320 --> 15:03.790
But it's you I want to protect more.

15:05.150 --> 15:05.910
Given that we came together,

15:05.940 --> 15:07.180
we must make it back together.

15:11.410 --> 15:12.330
Shuo.

15:12.350 --> 15:13.150
What's wrong?

15:14.160 --> 15:15.150
Nothing.

15:15.570 --> 15:17.090
Things are unpredictable tonight.

15:17.110 --> 15:18.100
You don't have to force yourself.

15:18.130 --> 15:19.280
I promised I will help you,

15:19.300 --> 15:20.650
and I will stand by that promise,

15:20.680 --> 15:21.800
no matter what happens.

15:26.310 --> 15:27.360
Nan Wan.

15:27.360 --> 15:28.550
Be polite.

15:31.340 --> 15:32.220
Thank you.

15:32.240 --> 15:33.350
Are you really drinking that?

15:34.130 --> 15:35.670
Hua Lin doesn't seem to be taking us

15:35.690 --> 15:37.260
Eternals and demons seriously, does he?

15:37.280 --> 15:38.840
He invited us to the banquet,

15:38.870 --> 15:40.110
but he is late himself.

15:40.810 --> 15:42.460
It's whatever the host prefers.

15:42.740 --> 15:45.060
As an Eternal, you should be more patient.

15:45.090 --> 15:46.850
If it weren't for the Wutong Spirit Pill,

15:46.870 --> 15:48.270
who would ever visit

15:48.300 --> 15:49.140
such a deserted place?

15:49.770 --> 15:50.530
Would you?

15:50.560 --> 15:52.080
His Majesty is here.

16:34.980 --> 16:37.410
Something came up today,

16:37.750 --> 16:38.830
which caused me to be late.

16:38.850 --> 16:40.210
I have been remiss in my duties to you all.

16:40.240 --> 16:41.080
Allow me to

16:41.100 --> 16:42.450
offer my apologies to everyone.

16:42.480 --> 16:44.400
There's no need to be so polite.

16:44.420 --> 16:45.860
Hurry up and burn the Wutong branch,

16:45.890 --> 16:47.800
so that we can summon the third Heart Flame,

16:47.830 --> 16:49.720
and select the winner of the Wutong Martial Arts Contest.

16:49.750 --> 16:51.290
I can't bear to

16:51.350 --> 16:52.350
stay in this

16:52.370 --> 16:54.050
Outlanders' City any longer.

16:54.080 --> 16:55.460
Don't worry, Divinity.

16:55.540 --> 16:56.740
The Wutong branch

16:56.760 --> 16:58.160
is in the wooden box.

16:58.870 --> 17:01.070
All of you joined the Wutong Martial Arts Contest

17:01.100 --> 17:02.790
to win the Wutong Spirit Pill.

17:03.840 --> 17:05.609
The winner tonight

17:06.079 --> 17:08.040
will win the pill.

17:08.060 --> 17:09.220
But I

17:09.359 --> 17:11.579
have something to tell you.

17:11.720 --> 17:12.880
I've decided hat

17:13.540 --> 17:14.780
from today onwards,

17:14.990 --> 17:16.339
I'll open up Outlanders' City

17:16.960 --> 17:18.349
and let the Outlanders entire the world.

17:18.980 --> 17:20.000
From now on,

17:20.240 --> 17:21.290
the Outlander Race

17:21.550 --> 17:22.599
will no longer

17:22.599 --> 17:24.319
be trapped in Outlanders' City.

17:24.619 --> 17:26.619
I ask that

17:26.650 --> 17:28.290
you relay my words

17:28.310 --> 17:29.750
to your sect after you return.

17:30.360 --> 17:31.000
In the future,

17:31.000 --> 17:32.580
as our Outlanders roam the world,

17:32.690 --> 17:33.890
I also ask for your

17:33.920 --> 17:35.130
kind attention and care,

17:35.160 --> 17:36.600
and not make things difficult for them.

17:39.280 --> 17:40.530
What are you even thinking?

17:40.560 --> 17:41.550
Empty talk from a fool.

17:43.690 --> 17:45.470
I know, right? What a joke.

17:45.500 --> 17:46.980
What? How is that possible?

17:48.750 --> 17:50.430
How can we stand with the Outlanders?

17:57.910 --> 17:59.040
Outside of Outlanders' City,

17:59.070 --> 18:00.980
the Eternals, demons and humans

18:01.000 --> 18:02.120
each have their own regions.

18:02.150 --> 18:03.870
How can there be any spare land for the Outlanders?

18:04.260 --> 18:06.020
If the Outlander Race wants to step out of Outlanders' City,

18:06.050 --> 18:08.240
you must have a blessed place to reside in.

18:08.260 --> 18:09.380
Would this place

18:09.410 --> 18:11.130
be carved out by us Eternals,

18:11.150 --> 18:12.670
or by the demons?

18:14.280 --> 18:16.520
We demons have no room

18:16.540 --> 18:18.140
to accomodate the Outlanders.

18:19.290 --> 18:22.560
You Outlanders are born with weaker spiritual powers.

18:22.780 --> 18:24.870
If you guys are living well in Outlanders' City,

18:24.890 --> 18:26.930
what's the point of wandering around?

18:26.960 --> 18:27.440
Right?

18:27.460 --> 18:28.340
Yeah.

18:30.450 --> 18:32.090
-Yeah.
-You've overestimated yourself.

18:32.940 --> 18:33.820
That's right.

18:34.900 --> 18:36.020
Are the Eternals and demons

18:36.040 --> 18:37.820
really unable to accommodate the Outlanders?

18:37.850 --> 18:38.920
Oppressing the weak with power.

18:38.950 --> 18:40.310
It's the same everywhere.

18:40.860 --> 18:41.900
Just now,

18:41.930 --> 18:43.290
what I said

18:43.320 --> 18:45.080
was just some of my thoughts.

18:45.100 --> 18:47.020
Since you all think it's inappropriate

18:47.050 --> 18:48.650
for Outlanders to enter the world,

18:49.140 --> 18:50.180
I will

18:50.210 --> 18:51.690
give it some more thought.

18:52.200 --> 18:53.150
Tonight,

18:53.350 --> 18:55.530
let's wrap up the contest first.

18:55.640 --> 18:57.040
As per the contest's traditions,

18:57.060 --> 18:57.780
we need

18:57.810 --> 18:59.420
the Three Races to gather

18:59.470 --> 19:00.990
and burn the Wutong branch together,

19:01.010 --> 19:03.810
in order to stimulate the third Heart Flame.

19:03.840 --> 19:05.040
Well...

19:16.430 --> 19:18.130
So this is the Wutong branch?

19:25.610 --> 19:26.590
Now,

19:26.780 --> 19:28.180
everybody, please

19:28.670 --> 19:30.440
burn the Wutong branch together.

19:45.590 --> 19:46.710
It's lit.

20:14.430 --> 20:15.370
Look!

20:15.390 --> 20:16.430
Look up!

20:18.920 --> 20:20.960
-Heart Flame?
-That's the Heart Flame!

20:22.060 --> 20:23.540
That's the third Heart Flame.

20:28.360 --> 20:29.620
It has finally appeared.

20:30.010 --> 20:31.440
What's going on?

20:37.950 --> 20:39.250
Your Majesty,

20:39.690 --> 20:41.330
why is the third Heart Flame

20:41.350 --> 20:43.230
looking so dull?

20:43.260 --> 20:45.180
This Wutong Martial Arts Contest hosted by the Outlanders

20:45.200 --> 20:46.800
is not a scam, is it?

20:47.390 --> 20:48.430
Indeed.

20:48.470 --> 20:50.550
The ritual is not over yet.

20:50.660 --> 20:51.580
Everyone,

20:51.690 --> 20:53.170
please calm down.

20:54.460 --> 20:56.020
May I ask Ms. Bai

20:56.050 --> 20:58.410
to hand over the two Heart Flames that are with you?

20:58.430 --> 20:59.430
-What?
-She has both Heart Flames?

20:59.460 --> 21:01.240
She has both Heart Flames?

21:03.400 --> 21:06.120
-How did Bai Shuo get both Heart Flames?
-Didn’t Mu Jiu have the Heart Flame previously?

21:06.140 --> 21:06.880
Heart Flame?

21:06.880 --> 21:07.680
Her?

21:07.680 --> 21:08.880
Hand over the Heart Flame. Give it up now!

21:11.230 --> 21:12.670
It seems that

21:12.690 --> 21:14.850
I can't hide anything from you, Your Majesty.

21:14.880 --> 21:16.940
Mu Jiu gave me this Heart Flame.

21:16.970 --> 21:18.330
Are there rules that state

21:18.350 --> 21:19.830
we are not allowed to give this Heart Flame to each other?

21:19.860 --> 21:21.140
Not really.

21:21.160 --> 21:22.670
Then what do you mean, Your Majesty?

21:22.690 --> 21:23.970
Are you trying to take back

21:24.000 --> 21:25.690
the Heart Flames that already have an owner?

21:25.770 --> 21:26.940
Of course not.

21:27.490 --> 21:28.990
The Wutong Heart Flame

21:29.020 --> 21:31.120
was created as one.

21:31.390 --> 21:33.090
The third Heart Flame

21:33.430 --> 21:35.030
needs the other two

21:35.050 --> 21:36.510
in order to be awakened.

21:37.900 --> 21:39.060
-Hand it over!
-Hand it over!

21:39.080 --> 21:40.410
-Hand it over!
-Hand it over!

21:40.480 --> 21:42.200
Hand over the other two Heart Flames!

21:42.440 --> 21:43.840
No one can own both of them.

21:43.840 --> 21:44.840
Just her?

21:44.840 --> 21:45.900
Give them up now!

21:46.640 --> 21:47.830
Hand it over!

21:57.290 --> 21:58.370
During the Fenlan Banquet,

21:58.390 --> 22:00.070
whether those Eternals or demons attend,

22:00.100 --> 22:01.010
the Bright Moon Palace

22:01.040 --> 22:02.810
would definitely be the focus of the King.

22:03.280 --> 22:04.480
I heard that the Fox Clan

22:04.500 --> 22:06.330
are best at hiding and running away.

22:06.350 --> 22:08.110
You shall first sneak into the Underground Palace tonight

22:08.140 --> 22:09.380
and see if Hua Yong is there.

22:09.400 --> 22:10.600
If he's not in the Underground Palace,

22:10.600 --> 22:12.600
try your best to bring him them.

22:13.090 --> 22:13.890
I got it.

22:14.940 --> 22:15.820
What about you?

22:15.850 --> 22:16.950
The third Heart Flame will be created after

22:16.980 --> 22:18.280
the Eternals, demons and the King of Outlanders

22:18.280 --> 22:19.670
burn the Wutong branch together.

22:19.690 --> 22:21.210
After we get the third Heart Flame,

22:21.240 --> 22:22.620
I'll meet you in the Underground Palace.

22:22.650 --> 22:23.650
No problem.

22:23.670 --> 22:24.810
Leave it to me.

22:24.840 --> 22:25.720
But,

22:25.740 --> 22:27.540
you have to prepare two things for me.

22:27.570 --> 22:29.250
One of it is the map of the palace,

22:29.270 --> 22:30.670
and the other is Hua Yong's portrait.

22:46.800 --> 22:47.400
This is...

22:59.780 --> 23:00.700
Look!

23:02.130 --> 23:02.960
The Heart Flame!

23:04.210 --> 23:04.850
The Heart Flame.

23:08.110 --> 23:09.230
It's fused together.

23:29.610 --> 23:31.850
Now that the three heart flames have come together,

23:31.880 --> 23:33.370
Your Majesty, please tell us

23:33.400 --> 23:35.730
how we'll be deciding the final winner.

23:36.960 --> 23:38.390
It's the Wutong Martial Arts Contest.

23:38.650 --> 23:40.490
Of course we'll need to fight.

23:54.120 --> 23:55.600
What are you doing? Do you want to fight?

23:55.600 --> 23:56.320
What are you doing?

23:58.240 --> 23:59.360
-What are you doing?
-What are you doing?

24:00.970 --> 24:01.970
Hua Lin.

24:02.390 --> 24:04.060
What exactly do you want?

24:04.690 --> 24:06.610
You Eternals and demons

24:06.630 --> 24:08.470
are full of hypocrisy,

24:08.500 --> 24:10.050
deceiving the world for your own glory.

24:10.150 --> 24:12.200
Since you despise the Outlander Race this much,

24:12.590 --> 24:13.950
I will

24:13.980 --> 24:15.320
kill al of you and bur your bones

24:15.320 --> 24:16.560
here in the Outlanders' City.

24:32.320 --> 24:33.660
What on earth is this place?

24:34.050 --> 24:35.370
It's so creepy.

24:43.260 --> 24:44.380
Hua Yong?

24:47.260 --> 24:48.070
Hua Yong?

24:49.150 --> 24:51.340
Did the King of Outlanders used evil magic to offer this sacrifice?

24:52.320 --> 24:53.400
Who is he offering this sacrifice to?

24:54.030 --> 24:54.610
No.

24:54.640 --> 24:55.760
This is too strange.

24:56.300 --> 24:57.950
I must not let Tian Huo and Bai Shuo in.

24:58.300 --> 24:59.420
I have to take Hua Yong away.

25:14.270 --> 25:16.080
Where do you want to take him?

25:16.350 --> 25:17.590
What are you doing?

25:17.620 --> 25:18.580
Let me tell you.

25:18.600 --> 25:20.000
I'm the young master of the Fox Clan.

25:20.030 --> 25:21.830
If anything happens to me here in Outlanders' City,

25:21.850 --> 25:23.930
my aunt will definitely come for all of you.

25:23.960 --> 25:25.790
As long as today's plans are successful,

25:25.910 --> 25:27.790
let alone Chang Mei,

25:27.820 --> 25:29.620
your entire clan could come

25:29.640 --> 25:31.620
and we Outlanders wouldn't even give a damn.

25:34.430 --> 25:35.910
Just now,

25:36.000 --> 25:38.530
I've given you one last chance.

25:38.630 --> 25:41.110
If you are willing to give us Outlanders a way out,

25:41.390 --> 25:42.630
I can also

25:42.660 --> 25:44.720
give you all a way out.

25:44.930 --> 25:46.010
But unfortunately,

25:46.030 --> 25:47.630
you didn't cherish the opportunity.

25:47.920 --> 25:49.480
Today's dire situation

25:49.740 --> 25:51.540
is entirely of your own making.

25:51.570 --> 25:52.470
Hua Lin.

25:52.570 --> 25:53.770
If you dare to act rashly,

25:53.800 --> 25:55.480
Bright Moon Palace will definitely not spare your life.

25:55.500 --> 25:56.860
You are restricted by the Magic Restriction,

25:57.810 --> 25:59.610
and you are also seriously injured.

25:59.630 --> 26:01.830
You don't have to pretend you're fine.

26:01.930 --> 26:03.410
At this point,

26:04.020 --> 26:04.970
tonight,

26:04.990 --> 26:06.630
I ask that

26:06.660 --> 26:08.140
you die here too.

26:08.160 --> 26:09.040
Hua Lin.

26:09.070 --> 26:10.710
Even if you kill all the Eternals and demons in the city today,

26:10.730 --> 26:12.470
it only brings you temporary relief.

26:12.490 --> 26:14.530
The Eternals and demons will seek their revenge one day.

26:14.560 --> 26:15.900
How can the Outlanders

26:15.920 --> 26:17.440
stand against the fury of the world?

26:18.070 --> 26:19.310
After tonight,

26:19.330 --> 26:20.530
we, the Outlander Race,

26:20.560 --> 26:23.190
will no longer be trapped in this lonely city

26:23.260 --> 26:25.710
and be bullied by the Eternals and demons ever again.

26:25.730 --> 26:26.830
As Outlanders,

26:26.850 --> 26:28.410
there'll be no place that is off-limits,

26:28.440 --> 26:29.990
and there'll be nothing we cannot do.

26:30.410 --> 26:31.830
All rules

26:31.950 --> 26:33.540
shall be decided by the Outlanders.

26:35.390 --> 26:36.610
Decided by the Outlanders?

26:36.810 --> 26:38.150
-On what grounds?
-Yeah.

26:39.610 --> 26:40.580
Who’s afraid of who?

26:41.000 --> 26:42.720
You are not just looking to vent your anger.

26:42.750 --> 26:44.360
What exactly do you intend to do with the lives

26:44.380 --> 26:46.030
of all these Eternals and demons?

26:46.100 --> 26:47.660
Don't worry.

26:47.690 --> 26:48.770
Soon,

26:48.790 --> 26:50.310
you will know the answer.

26:51.470 --> 26:52.380
Your Majesty,

26:52.550 --> 26:54.080
I advise you to stop now.

26:54.510 --> 26:56.450
The Lanling disciples are at the inn.

26:56.710 --> 26:58.110
Once they figure out something is wrong,

26:58.140 --> 26:59.570
they will report to the sect immediately.

26:59.680 --> 27:00.760
Within tonight,

27:00.780 --> 27:01.780
the Five Eternals of Lanling

27:01.810 --> 27:03.130
will arrive in Outlanders' City.

27:03.160 --> 27:04.640
I

27:04.660 --> 27:06.230
forgot to tell you.

27:06.400 --> 27:08.880
The Outlanders' City's barrier has been activated.

27:08.900 --> 27:10.720
No one from outside can get in,

27:11.270 --> 27:12.610
and no one from inside

27:12.810 --> 27:14.330
can similarly get out.

27:21.250 --> 27:22.650
How are we going to get out then?

27:23.930 --> 27:24.830
Tonight,

27:24.980 --> 27:26.990
you'll only die here in Outlanders' City.

27:27.260 --> 27:28.510
Take them down!

27:40.100 --> 27:41.190
Get the Heart Flame!

27:50.560 --> 27:51.480
Heart Flame!

27:52.420 --> 27:54.160
Let's get out of here!

28:29.460 --> 28:30.120
Zhao.

28:30.140 --> 28:31.020
Are you okay?

28:31.050 --> 28:32.050
I'm fine.

28:32.070 --> 28:32.790
Let's get out first.

28:32.820 --> 28:34.070
Do what you have to do.

28:34.730 --> 28:35.370
Let's go.

28:39.850 --> 28:40.530
Let's go.

28:58.290 --> 28:59.090
There's no time.

28:59.110 --> 29:00.430
Hurry and get vision from the Contemplation Stone.

29:00.460 --> 29:01.660
Only by breaking Hua Lin's scheme

29:01.680 --> 29:02.770
can we save everyone.

29:02.800 --> 29:03.720
You go to the Underground Palace.

29:03.740 --> 29:05.080
I'll distract Hua Lin.

29:26.930 --> 29:27.890
If you don't stop,

29:27.920 --> 29:29.600
I'll destroy these three Heart Flames immediately.

29:30.890 --> 29:32.410
You think you can threaten me

29:32.430 --> 29:34.010
with just these three Heart Flames?

29:34.340 --> 29:36.540
If these three Heart Flames are not important,

29:36.570 --> 29:38.690
why did you drop everything and come after me?

29:39.250 --> 29:40.820
The Eternals and demons had already fallen for your trap.

29:40.840 --> 29:42.560
You could have simply ordered for our arrest,

29:42.590 --> 29:43.950
but you just had to retrieve the first two Heart Flames

29:43.970 --> 29:45.210
from Bai Shuo.

29:45.400 --> 29:46.450
This proves

29:46.650 --> 29:48.680
you also need these three Heart Flames.

29:49.170 --> 29:50.500
Even if you know,

29:50.860 --> 29:51.780
so what?

29:51.800 --> 29:53.720
No one can stop my plans.

30:06.130 --> 30:07.900
Your plans

30:07.980 --> 30:09.430
are doomed to fail.

30:11.250 --> 30:12.210
I've already made my arrangements

30:12.240 --> 30:13.530
in the Underground Palace.

30:13.560 --> 30:15.080
Do you think you can stop everything

30:15.100 --> 30:16.610
just by luring me away?

30:16.630 --> 30:18.270
What exactly do you want?

30:18.300 --> 30:19.700
Given that the situation is settled,

30:20.100 --> 30:21.730
I can now tell you.

30:22.250 --> 30:22.970
I want

30:22.990 --> 30:24.550
all of the Eternals and demons in the city to become offerings,

30:25.210 --> 30:26.910
so as to make Yong a deity.

30:38.530 --> 30:39.890
Sacrificial altar?

30:42.440 --> 30:43.680
Where is Mu Jiu?

30:43.820 --> 30:45.060
Did he fail to come in

30:45.080 --> 30:46.340
or did something happened?

30:48.140 --> 30:49.910
This is the third scene from the Contemplation Stone.

30:50.320 --> 30:51.430
We are here in the Underground Palace,

30:51.620 --> 30:52.700
we have three Heart Flames,

30:53.750 --> 30:54.630
Hua Yong,

30:56.280 --> 30:57.160
and you.

30:57.840 --> 30:58.870
All conditions have been met.

30:58.900 --> 31:00.230
Why is there no response?

31:01.030 --> 31:02.610
Are we missing something?

31:13.880 --> 31:16.440
You've gone crazy.

31:16.530 --> 31:18.090
Zhen Yu is a sinister man.

31:18.120 --> 31:19.480
You have no idea what might

31:19.480 --> 31:20.840
emerge from evil magic.

31:20.930 --> 31:21.730
Do you know

31:21.750 --> 31:23.230
if you take just one wrong step,

31:24.000 --> 31:25.880
he won't even have

31:25.880 --> 31:27.170
the chance to live?

31:27.200 --> 31:28.730
If I don't do this,

31:29.540 --> 31:31.340
Yong won't get to live for long either.

31:32.250 --> 31:33.250
There will be no Outlander

31:33.280 --> 31:35.240
who can wield the Outlander King's Sword.

31:36.090 --> 31:37.090
By then, we Outlanders

31:38.140 --> 31:39.900
will be in dire straits.

31:41.570 --> 31:42.730
One day,

31:43.510 --> 31:45.030
you will understand my choice.

31:45.050 --> 31:47.580
You're always so full of yourself.

31:47.870 --> 31:49.060
Whether it was seven years ago

31:49.120 --> 31:50.480
or seven years later,

31:50.510 --> 31:52.570
even though you knew that sacrificing mother

31:52.590 --> 31:54.350
would not eliminate the famine,

31:54.380 --> 31:55.680
you still would not dare to go against the people's will

31:55.720 --> 31:57.350
to protect her.

31:57.380 --> 31:58.020
Now,

31:58.040 --> 31:59.440
you know full well that making Hua Yong a deity

31:59.470 --> 32:01.030
wouldn't truly solve

32:01.050 --> 32:02.010
the Outlanders' discrimination,

32:02.040 --> 32:03.520
yet you refuse to face the truth.

32:03.900 --> 32:04.940
Hua Lin.

32:05.360 --> 32:06.920
You are just a coward.

32:07.360 --> 32:09.480
A complete and utter coward!

32:12.760 --> 32:14.200
When I was young,

32:15.370 --> 32:17.480
I used to ride on your neck,

32:18.730 --> 32:20.970
and I even stood on your shoulders

32:21.720 --> 32:24.080
to reach out of the stars in the sky.

32:24.100 --> 32:25.380
At that time,

32:26.450 --> 32:28.860
I really thought my father

32:29.030 --> 32:32.050
was the strongest hero in the world.

32:31.340 --> 32:36.300
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

32:33.460 --> 32:34.830
But why...

32:35.480 --> 32:38.480
Why did you become like this?

32:39.330 --> 32:40.610
I've never

32:39.460 --> 32:45.090
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

32:42.880 --> 32:44.800
given up on your mother.

32:45.360 --> 32:47.440
I tried my best to save her.

32:47.460 --> 32:48.540
Save her?

32:47.750 --> 32:55.180
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

32:49.320 --> 32:52.230
It was you who made her jump into the furnace.

32:52.780 --> 32:54.140
The plan we had discussed

32:54.160 --> 32:55.490
was for your mother to fake her death

32:55.520 --> 32:57.510
so as to reassure the people.

32:55.940 --> 33:01.150
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

32:58.380 --> 32:59.440
What did you say?

33:00.470 --> 33:01.750
Fake her death?

33:02.350 --> 33:04.190
I gave her the Fire Protection Pearl,

33:05.040 --> 33:06.640
and left a escape passage

33:06.660 --> 33:08.140
under the furnace.

33:08.170 --> 33:09.680
She should have been able to survive.

33:11.310 --> 33:12.930
Burn her to death!

33:13.390 --> 33:14.510
But,

33:15.100 --> 33:16.620
something went wrong.

33:17.860 --> 33:19.320
We were just one step away,

33:20.450 --> 33:24.010
♫Across thousands of miles♫

33:22.150 --> 33:23.640
but it cause me,

33:24.050 --> 33:25.520
you,

33:25.690 --> 33:26.930
and Yong

33:28.780 --> 33:33.470
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

33:28.920 --> 33:30.560
to lose her forever.

33:30.590 --> 33:31.790
Mother!

33:31.840 --> 33:33.560
No!

33:33.560 --> 33:35.680
Don't!

33:36.100 --> 33:43.370
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

33:38.820 --> 33:40.380
So what went wrong?

33:41.090 --> 33:43.290
Wu Zhao was tricked by a sorcerer.

33:44.230 --> 33:45.980
The Fire Protection Pearl he gave me

33:44.440 --> 33:49.340
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

33:47.020 --> 33:48.100
was fake.

33:49.150 --> 33:50.270
Wu Zhao?

33:57.410 --> 33:58.390
Princess,

33:58.530 --> 33:59.940
are you calling for me?

34:05.750 --> 34:07.350
Why are you here?

34:08.239 --> 34:10.190
Didn't I tell you to guard the Underground Palace?

34:10.310 --> 34:11.830
The Underground Palace is under control.

34:13.179 --> 34:13.699
No.

34:14.370 --> 34:15.210
In other words,

34:15.230 --> 34:16.750
the whole Outlanders' City has been controlled,

34:17.060 --> 34:18.420
including you, Your Majesty,

34:19.219 --> 34:20.219
and the Princess.

34:20.610 --> 34:21.580
Wu Zhao.

34:22.060 --> 34:23.120
What do you mean?

34:23.699 --> 34:25.050
A long time ago,

34:25.080 --> 34:26.130
I thought to myself,

34:26.659 --> 34:27.850
you were born weak

34:27.880 --> 34:29.159
and indecisive.

34:29.800 --> 34:30.960
You could wield the Outlander King's Sword

34:30.960 --> 34:32.280
all thanks to the Mei family's help.

34:32.300 --> 34:33.980
No matter how I see it,

34:34.290 --> 34:35.639
you are just not as good as me.

34:35.770 --> 34:38.090
What makes you worthy of being the king of this Outlanders' City,

34:38.110 --> 34:39.469
while I am not?

34:39.500 --> 34:41.000
How dare you!

34:55.310 --> 34:57.550
You've been hiding your power all this time.

34:58.430 --> 34:59.510
You...

34:59.530 --> 35:01.830
didn't use an Outlanders' techniques.

35:02.250 --> 35:03.530
Where did you

35:04.430 --> 35:06.230
learn those evil techniques from?

35:06.260 --> 35:08.150
You can work with Cold Spring Palace,

35:08.640 --> 35:10.120
so why can't I?

35:11.740 --> 35:13.520
You were the one

35:14.140 --> 35:15.330
who saved Fu Ling last night.

35:16.340 --> 35:18.490
At this point, I don't have to hide it anymore.

35:18.510 --> 35:20.190
It's a grand celebration tonight.

35:21.520 --> 35:23.310
I not only want the life of the Eternals and demons,

35:23.550 --> 35:24.680
but also

35:25.440 --> 35:26.670
your life.

35:30.400 --> 35:31.800
I said

35:31.820 --> 35:33.290
I'll see you again.

35:35.570 --> 35:37.070
Why do you have spiritual power?

35:37.400 --> 35:39.480
If you Eternals and demons can work together,

35:39.500 --> 35:40.900
of course I'll also have my allies

35:40.930 --> 35:42.490
in Outlanders' City.

35:43.120 --> 35:44.040
Why?

35:44.290 --> 35:45.770
Do you regret

35:45.790 --> 35:46.910
not killing me last night?

35:46.940 --> 35:48.100
-Don’t touch her!
-Don’t touch her!

35:53.620 --> 35:55.530
One is the Polar Region's Demon King,

35:56.280 --> 35:57.880
and the other is the head disciple of Lanling.

35:57.900 --> 35:59.540
Both are willing to sacrifice their lives for you.

35:59.570 --> 36:00.530
Bai Shuo,

36:00.550 --> 36:02.380
you are indeed quite something.

36:02.570 --> 36:03.570
Last night, your sword

36:03.600 --> 36:04.940
was stained with my blood.

36:04.970 --> 36:06.090
Do you think I should

36:06.110 --> 36:08.110
avenge with blood too?

36:08.140 --> 36:10.080
Why don't you kill me immediately instead?

36:12.280 --> 36:14.240
You are only this fearless because

36:14.260 --> 36:16.700
you know that the Contemplation Stone is in your body.

36:16.730 --> 36:18.410
If I kill you by force,

36:18.430 --> 36:19.950
wouldn't I suffer from the backlash of its divine power?

36:20.800 --> 36:22.120
I don't like

36:22.120 --> 36:23.590
your petty tricks.

36:23.650 --> 36:24.450
No.

36:24.490 --> 36:25.870
Actually,

36:26.280 --> 36:27.560
I don't like

36:27.580 --> 36:28.950
all of you.

36:29.030 --> 36:29.870
Why are you

36:29.890 --> 36:32.040
relentlessly cornering me,

36:32.070 --> 36:34.000
and even forcing the person who was most important to me to die?

36:34.030 --> 36:35.480
Is it all because of the Contemplation Stone?

36:36.890 --> 36:39.210
It's not just because of that,

36:39.230 --> 36:41.270
but also because

36:41.300 --> 36:42.820
your happiness

36:42.840 --> 36:44.170
seems too jarring.

36:45.030 --> 36:46.660
You probably don't know that

36:46.750 --> 36:48.390
the first time we met

36:48.420 --> 36:50.340
wasn't at the Governor's Mansion,

36:50.360 --> 36:52.330
but at the Unbridled Pavilion.

37:00.600 --> 37:01.990
You were so full of vigor

37:02.010 --> 37:03.780
and so carefree.

37:03.810 --> 37:05.320
Back then, I thought

37:05.340 --> 37:07.160
such a carefree person

37:07.180 --> 37:09.070
deserve to suffer more.

37:09.290 --> 37:10.370
Crazy.

37:10.390 --> 37:11.390
Crazy?

37:12.480 --> 37:13.840
To me, that sounds like

37:13.860 --> 37:15.160
a compliment.

37:15.180 --> 37:16.540
In this world,

37:16.570 --> 37:17.930
rather than being a good person,

37:17.960 --> 37:19.430
I'd rather be a madman.

37:19.460 --> 37:20.620
At least, I'm happy.

37:21.740 --> 37:23.060
For example,

37:23.080 --> 37:24.920
I just want to play a game with you now.

37:26.130 --> 37:27.730
A city full of Eternals and demons,

37:27.750 --> 37:28.950
all caught up in the net

37:28.980 --> 37:30.270
for the blood sacrifice tonight.

37:30.290 --> 37:31.570
Your death is near,

37:32.320 --> 37:34.200
but I can give you a chance.

37:35.040 --> 37:36.180
Between Fan Yue

37:36.210 --> 37:37.530
and Chong Zho,

37:37.640 --> 37:38.780
pick one.

37:39.060 --> 37:40.580
Whoever you choose,

37:40.610 --> 37:41.930
I can let him go.

37:45.590 --> 37:46.430
Shuo.

37:46.450 --> 37:47.610
Don't believe her.

37:50.590 --> 37:51.630
Fan Yue!

37:51.740 --> 37:53.260
I don't need you to believe me.

37:53.280 --> 37:54.850
I just need you to choose.

37:55.050 --> 37:56.390
If you don't choose,

37:56.660 --> 37:58.340
both of them will die.

38:01.690 --> 38:02.730
Bai Shuo,

38:02.750 --> 38:04.630
you claim to be a man of honor.

38:04.660 --> 38:06.250
I'm curious to see

38:06.280 --> 38:07.680
how you will choose

38:07.700 --> 38:09.060
between two difficult choices?

38:10.990 --> 38:12.360
What should we do?

38:12.590 --> 38:13.500
We can't get out.

38:14.630 --> 38:16.350
How can we break through this barrier?

38:16.440 --> 38:18.000
Stop complaining and think of something.

38:20.770 --> 38:23.250
I didn't expect that attending the Wutong Martial Arts Contest

38:23.270 --> 38:25.210
would cost me my life.

38:25.420 --> 38:26.880
Ms. Bai did remind me that

38:26.880 --> 38:28.000
the banquet will be dangerous.

38:29.070 --> 38:30.950
I'm here on my master's order.

38:31.800 --> 38:32.600
So why are you here?

38:32.600 --> 38:33.960
Why did you come when you knew it was dangerous?

38:35.590 --> 38:37.270
Why did you save me just now?

38:38.800 --> 38:40.840
The various sects of the Eternals are meant to stay united.

38:40.860 --> 38:42.560
You haven’t answered my question.

38:44.700 --> 38:45.730
What a pity.

38:45.940 --> 38:47.060
What's a pity?

38:47.800 --> 38:48.760
I...

38:50.220 --> 38:51.480
have a younger brother.

38:51.690 --> 38:53.050
He was born with a weak spiritual vein.

38:53.080 --> 38:54.280
He won't be able to live long.

38:54.850 --> 38:56.490
I heard that this Wutong Spirit Pill

38:57.190 --> 38:58.780
can repair the spiritual vein.

38:58.820 --> 38:59.890
So...

39:00.590 --> 39:01.710
So that's the reason for

39:01.730 --> 39:03.370
your rash and hasty behaviour earlier.

39:04.720 --> 39:05.640
It's all for naught.

39:05.760 --> 39:06.480
How long have you

39:06.500 --> 39:07.860
been planning for this day?

39:07.980 --> 39:08.980
For how long?

39:10.370 --> 39:12.650
From the day I was adopted by the Mei family,

39:12.670 --> 39:14.880
I haven't had a day where I didn't think about rising to power.

39:15.660 --> 39:17.380
You were born a prince.

39:17.410 --> 39:18.410
No matter how weak you are,

39:18.440 --> 39:19.880
people will do everything

39:19.880 --> 39:20.920
to make you a king.

39:21.290 --> 39:22.210
And I,

39:22.230 --> 39:23.470
being born at the bottom,

39:24.270 --> 39:26.040
have been bullied since I was young.

39:26.120 --> 39:27.640
I asked why,

39:27.670 --> 39:28.870
but they told me

39:30.050 --> 39:31.570
this is my life.

39:31.590 --> 39:32.950
A wretched life.

39:37.420 --> 39:38.990
These scars

39:39.250 --> 39:40.810
were not incurred on the battlefield,

39:41.660 --> 39:43.260
but from Outlanders.

39:43.810 --> 39:45.410
I was homeless when I was young.

39:45.430 --> 39:46.910
I've had enough of people's evil.

39:47.810 --> 39:49.630
I had to rely on the Mei family to make a comeback.

39:49.870 --> 39:51.160
That's why I became a tool for the Mei family

39:51.160 --> 39:52.760
to protect the royal family.

39:53.420 --> 39:55.940
Grandfather treats you like his own child.

39:56.720 --> 39:58.890
Mother treats you like her own brother.

39:59.440 --> 40:00.680
How could you be so cold?

40:00.760 --> 40:01.660
Cold?

40:01.780 --> 40:03.790
When your mother was forced to die,

40:03.870 --> 40:05.230
who wasn't cold?

40:07.150 --> 40:08.510
Speaking of Mei Han,

40:08.690 --> 40:10.410
she did treat me well.

40:11.770 --> 40:13.090
But unfortunately,

40:13.290 --> 40:15.330
she's a blocker in my path to becoming king,

40:15.500 --> 40:17.000
so she has to die.

40:18.400 --> 40:20.160
What did you do to her?

40:21.150 --> 40:23.620
Blame her for being too smart.

40:24.250 --> 40:26.280
Seven years ago, there was a famine in Outlanders' City.

40:26.360 --> 40:28.470
I instigated the people to overthrow Hua Lin,

40:28.720 --> 40:30.300
but she found out.

40:30.610 --> 40:31.490
Do you think

40:32.140 --> 40:33.580
I could still keep her?

40:35.650 --> 40:37.090
In order to kill her, I just had to

40:37.120 --> 40:39.020
use a stone with the engraved words,

40:39.050 --> 40:40.370
"After the queen falls, the famine will be gone."

40:40.400 --> 40:42.760
But I underestimated your love for her.

40:44.080 --> 40:45.780
In the face of the people's demands,

40:46.110 --> 40:48.470
you chose to send her away and hide her.

40:48.860 --> 40:50.980
I had to change my plan.

40:53.040 --> 40:54.650
It's you.

40:55.340 --> 40:56.760
You used Hua Yong?

40:56.760 --> 40:57.470
Yes.

40:57.490 --> 40:59.450
The one who exposed your mother's hiding place

40:59.480 --> 41:00.520
was not Hua Yong.

41:02.210 --> 41:03.250
It was me.

41:03.830 --> 41:04.970
It was also me

41:05.000 --> 41:06.440
who pinned the blame to Hua Yong.

41:07.280 --> 41:08.600
I just didn't expect that

41:08.620 --> 41:10.690
when Mei Han stood up to face everything,

41:10.710 --> 41:12.640
you were still trying to protect her.

41:14.140 --> 41:16.620
I could only lie that I found the Fire Protection Pearl

41:16.750 --> 41:18.790
and suggested for Mei Han to fake her death.

41:19.000 --> 41:20.680
You believed me,

41:20.710 --> 41:22.150
and Mei Han threw herself into the furnace,

41:22.170 --> 41:23.390
taking all the secrets with her

41:23.410 --> 41:24.890
and dying completely.

41:25.330 --> 41:27.130
Then, I just claimed that I was deceived by a sorcerer,

41:27.150 --> 41:29.120
and didn't know that the Fire Protection Pearl was fake.

41:30.010 --> 41:31.330
You believed it too.

41:31.350 --> 41:33.070
I didn't blame you then

41:33.100 --> 41:35.220
because you're Mei Han's sworn brother.

41:35.240 --> 41:37.480
I didn't know you were such a beast.

41:37.510 --> 41:38.830
I'll kill you!

41:44.000 --> 41:48.960
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

41:52.120 --> 41:57.980
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

42:00.440 --> 42:07.840
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

42:05.090 --> 42:06.050
You mustn't die!

42:06.070 --> 42:07.550
I haven't forgiven you yet.

42:07.580 --> 42:08.700
I won't let you die.

42:08.720 --> 42:10.120
You can't die.

42:08.760 --> 42:13.950
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

42:10.710 --> 42:12.870
Hua Lin was indeed a good father.

42:13.110 --> 42:15.870
Seven years ago, you tried to wield the the Sword and destroy the city,

42:15.900 --> 42:17.380
but got wounded by the sword's energy.

42:17.400 --> 42:19.420
Did you think it was mere luck that you survived?

42:20.100 --> 42:22.460
It was Hua Lin who sent you out of the city for medical treatment,

42:22.480 --> 42:23.680
in order to save your life.

42:23.710 --> 42:25.550
It was only then you had the fortune of meeting Fan Yue.

42:26.460 --> 42:28.880
Why didn't you tell me?

42:30.000 --> 42:32.620
I want you to leave the Outlanders' City,

42:33.090 --> 42:36.650
♫Across thousands of miles♫

42:34.350 --> 42:38.200
and live a carefree life.

42:38.230 --> 42:40.100
I don't want to repeat

42:40.300 --> 42:42.860
your mother's tragedy.

42:41.330 --> 42:46.200
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

42:43.620 --> 42:45.260
No, no, don't die!

42:45.620 --> 42:46.660
Don't die!

42:46.750 --> 42:47.950
Father!

42:48.940 --> 42:55.870
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

42:49.600 --> 42:51.120
Don't die, Father!

42:51.140 --> 42:52.860
Don't die! Don't die!

42:57.020 --> 43:02.090
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

43:00.880 --> 43:03.430
Hearing you call me father,

43:05.460 --> 43:08.290
I can die without regrets.

43:17.810 --> 43:19.710
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

43:19.880 --> 43:22.010
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

43:22.070 --> 43:23.860
♫My love brought tears♫

43:23.600 --> 43:25.560
Father!

43:24.110 --> 43:25.880
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

43:26.140 --> 43:28.080
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

43:27.040 --> 43:28.800
No!

43:28.290 --> 43:29.510
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

43:29.750 --> 43:31.540
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

43:31.680 --> 43:33.240
No!

43:31.910 --> 43:33.890
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

43:34.250 --> 43:35.830
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

43:36.080 --> 43:37.730
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

43:38.000 --> 43:40.110
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

43:40.420 --> 43:42.000
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

43:42.320 --> 43:44.110
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

43:44.380 --> 43:46.390
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

43:46.680 --> 43:48.180
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

43:48.380 --> 43:50.840
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

44:03.960 --> 44:05.310
Mei Han said I was wrong.

44:06.660 --> 44:08.260
Hua Lin said I was wrong.

44:08.280 --> 44:10.170
Even you said I was wrong.

44:10.920 --> 44:13.480
Today, I will show you exactly

44:13.510 --> 44:16.060
who can save the Outlanders' City.

44:22.660 --> 44:24.000
Still undecided?

44:24.130 --> 44:25.850
I'm not that patient.

44:25.870 --> 44:26.890
I'll count to three.

44:26.920 --> 44:28.040
If you don't choose,

44:28.040 --> 44:29.120
you'll have no choice.

44:31.080 --> 44:32.160
One.

44:36.000 --> 44:36.760
Two.

44:41.120 --> 44:41.960
Three.
